## Entschlüsselung
```fish
# 1. Derived Key generieren
cd /mr-bytez/shared/deployment
fish derive_key.fish secrets

# 2. Secret entschlüsseln
age -d shared/.secrets/ssh/mrohwer/id_ed25519_github.age > /tmp/key
# → Passphrase = Derived Key eingeben

# 3. Key an Zielort kopieren
cp /tmp/key ~/.secrets/ssh/id_ed25519_github
chmod 600 ~/.secrets/ssh/id_ed25519_github
rm /tmp/key
```

